    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Great Car Ready for Its Next Owner!** If you're looking for a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that delivers real value, look no further! This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, looks great, and has been taken care of. You'll notice it has the minor signs of normal use you'd expect from a well-loved car, but nothing that gets in the way of a fantastic driving experience. No surprises here \u2014 just a trustworthy ride at a fair price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer who understands they are purchasing a project car or a basic transportation option. The car shows significant wear, including visible body damage, a worn interior, and mechanical issues that will require attention. It is drivable but should be inspected by a mechanic before purchase, as repairs and maintenance will likely be needed in the near term. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect these realities, and represents an opportunity for a handy buyer, mechanic, or someone seeking a low-cost vehicle who is comfortable taking it as-is.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $45,000, a price that genuinely reflects its outstanding mint condition \u2014 and we stand fully behind that assessment. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint shines with a deep, uniform luster, the body panels are straight and free of dents, scratches, or rust, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the upholstery, dashboard, and all surfaces show no meaningful wear, fading, or damage, presenting almost as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is in top-tier shape: the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises to report. All electronics, climate controls, and safety features operate flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle in genuinely exceptional condition \u2014 buyers can expect a car that requires no immediate repairs or reconditioning and is ready to be driven with confidence from day one.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Real Talk, Real Deal \u2014 A Budget Runner for the Practical Buyer! This used car is in poor condition, and we're being completely straight with you \u2014 it's got its share of wear, age, and accumulated miles that show. That said, it's the kind of vehicle that can serve a budget-conscious buyer who needs basic transportation and isn't afraid of a little TLC. No smoke and mirrors here \u2014 just an honest price for an honest car. If you're looking for something to get you from A to B without breaking the bank, this could be your ticket!",
      "price": 5750.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 it is sold strictly as-is and is best suited for buyers who are comfortable taking on a project car or need it for parts. The exterior shows visible damage including rust, dents, and faded or peeling paint that goes beyond cosmetic concerns. The interior is worn and shows signs of neglect, with damaged upholstery, broken trim pieces, and likely non-functional components. Mechanically, this car has known issues and should be expected to require significant repairs before it can be reliably driven \u2014 do not purchase this vehicle expecting a daily driver without substantial investment. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged, and we will make the car available for review. This is an honest listing for a buyer who knows what they're getting into and sees value in a vehicle at this price point.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
